This project is a derivative theme branch based on astro-blog-zozo by Ladit:
https://github.com/ladit/astro-blog-zozo

astro-blog-zozo was inspired by hugo-theme-zozo by varkai:
https://github.com/varkai/hugo-theme-zozo

Revamped Astro Zozo extends the upstream project with revised layouts, a gallery system, a friends page, updated navigation interactions, a sample-first content structure, and documentation intended for a public starter-kit style release.

